{"tid":499673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【奪命車禍】死者女友fb哀悼：你的願望由我代你完成","createTime":"2017-12-15T05:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T14:02:18.000Z","uid":160094,"like":4,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"0099c1b6a93f28e93299b9e9241b4167a055d9e7","tid":499673,"uid":160094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:41:04.000Z","msg":"【13：28更新】新增影片<br />\n「點解要Dum低我一個！」葵涌貨櫃碼頭南路凌晨發生致命車禍，23歲鐵騎士李寬耀，與數名朋友各自駕駛電單車遊車河。他本來載同女友同行，惟其間試駕朋友的電單車，結果途中出事，他傷重身亡，朋友昏迷垂危。車禍後女友陪伴送院，望着男友滿臉鮮血，只能默默祈禱，可惜最終男友傷重不治，頓時哭成淚人。直至早上7時，經過整夜的淚水洗臉，女友堅強地承諾：「你的願望，由我代你完成！」<br />\n<br />\n死者洋名Frankie，與重傷的姓馮男友人，均居於港島區。Frankie曾做救生員，從他的facebook所見，他熱愛攝影，亦喜歡駕乘電單車在馬路上風馳電掣，遂將兩元素結合，曾捱着眼瞓，一連四日，在返工前，與友人往大帽山結伴遊車河，並以專業的相機鏡頭，拍下一張張動感照。<br />\n死者的女友在其熏陶下，亦愛上駕乘電單車，死者曾在fb分享與女友在道路上駕駛的喜悅，「喜歡你天真的微笑&hellip;&hellip;喜歡與你分享我的速度與激情&hellip;&hellip;」可惜此情此景再不復在。<br />\n死者有超過3年駕駛電單車經驗，曾在fb透露於今年9月首次駕車失事跌倒，「人生第一次跌車，仲諗住可以保持不跌記錄，點知地濕，跣一跣腳就由0變1。」惟今日凌晨的一宗車禍，卻失去了寶貴的性命。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171215/large/1513308877_27ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171215%2Flarge%2F1513308877_27ce.jpg&h=cdd75abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n死者曾坐在警車上留影。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be429887e207ea2e59e27e37fdcdd156e65ee72a","tid":499673,"uid":160094,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171215/large/1513272370_dfa9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171215%2Flarge%2F1513272370_dfa9.jpg&h=bf81be83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電單車撞貨車尾及向攝入車底．嚴重損毀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171215/large/1513276366_a1d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171215%2Flarge%2F1513276366_a1d3.jpg&h=a792a45b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07b89c351e50fc6b9e3dc6211d52e20213d2cefc","tid":499673,"uid":45749,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:45:29.000Z","msg":"人包鐵"},{"pid":"6f487ee3854c25ad6d116f6e5ab488116ff93826","tid":499673,"uid":32723,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人包鐵</blockquote><br />\n皮包鐵"},{"pid":"d4796dd2bd828af1969ae6b94e8d9de69495d60d","tid":499673,"uid":40763,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:54:03.000Z","msg":"唔飲水會唔會冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529b267e5c898def32f5da12014187d991895598","tid":499673,"uid":35696,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:59:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔飲水會唔會冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呀婆實鬧死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37aef2652ca6a8df53a1f799c0a69366338c7c4","tid":499673,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26a80037f8d7682da6fa64589a231b58aad558c","tid":499673,"uid":160094,"like":116,"dislike":2,"score":114,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171215/large/1513272370_dfa9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171215%2Flarge%2F1513272370_dfa9.jpg&h=bf81be83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n架貨車公司名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\